        public void monitorStart(java.lang.String directory,
                         boolean force,
                         boolean resume)
        Start monitoring.
        Parameters:
        directory - path to directory in which store the monitoring file
        force - clear out existing training data from this directory (by deleting every file prefixed with "openaigym.")
        resume - retain the training data already in this directory, which will be merged with our new data
